{"tid":1699391,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"北約秘書長稱歐美要聯手評估中國技術變革對安全的影響","createTime":"2019-11-08T04:17:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T02:23:52.000Z","uid":141151,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"098ee41eacf7086647e639c21c713c171a811190","tid":1699391,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T04:17:57.000Z","msg":"北約秘書長稱歐美要聯手評估中國技術變革對安全的影響<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1490676-20191108.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1490676-20191108.htm&d=6wykgBqlsxypO2QI0oCEUn6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=ac567191\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1490676-20191108.htm&h=b7c107f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1490676-20191108.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n北約秘書長斯托爾滕貝格說，中國的軍事、經濟及技術地位，不斷提升，歐洲及美國需要聯手評估這個情況為安全帶來的影響。<br />\n<br />\n斯托爾滕貝格說，中國很快成為世界上最大經濟體，中國的國防預算，已經排名世界第二，而在創新領域，中國正投入大量人力物力。<br />\n<br />\n他說從5G到人臉辨識、從量子計算到大數據，中國正逐步成為全球新技術發展的領導者之一，歐美需要認清中國的崛起、驚人的技術變革步伐、及日益擴大的影響力，對安全、自由、民主及法治有甚麼意義，歐美要共同應對未來挑戰。"},{"pid":"f3da09944bc688266866886309c35ea6673b11ae","tid":1699391,"uid":14918,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T04:19:15.000Z","msg":"挪威人都開始醒"},{"pid":"4406b437e42154b65a50712382cd75f8d40dde79","tid":1699391,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T04:20:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">需要 Rt + like + reply</span><br />\n（求手動置頂）英國戰線Twitter要人！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1698490\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1698490</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a9624dfa9dc117d62f8bfaa916ca00e5a1cbcf69","tid":1699391,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:15:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89f292e646b412868